<br>
The strategy is to buy the cheapest horse (around 8500 plat) and TURN OFF HORSE MODELS so you don't have the annoying horsehead in your face, you don't have the annoying start/stop momentum, and you can use SOW speed, which is faster than the slowest nag.<br>
<br>
Then when you engage an enemy, sic the pet on him and JBB.  Do NOT turn on autoattack.  You'll actually be medding while CASTING on the creature.  This is a huge, huge advantage - trading one swipe with a weapon every 8 seconds for 8 seconds of medding.<br>
<br>
